graph LR
    DSP["Data Science Pipelines<br/>(KFP v2)"]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSP -->|"execution engine<br/>CRD Watch + Create"| ArgoWF["Argo Workflows<br/>v3.7.11"]
    DSP -->|"metadata persistence<br/>SQL 3306/5432"| Database["MySQL 5.7+ /<br/>PostgreSQL 12+"]
